                                <td class="text-neon-coral font-bold">NEW</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 bg-yellow-50">
                                <td class="py-1.5 pr-2 font-mono font-bold">UserInputService</td>
                                <td class="pr-2">키보드·마우스·터치 입력 감지. <code>InputBegan</code>으로 키 눌림 감지, <code>IsKeyDown()</code>으로 현재 상태 확인</td>
                                <td class="text-neon-coral font-bold">NEW</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="border-b border-gray-100 bg-yellow-50">
                                <td class="py-1.5 pr-2 font-mono font-bold">ReplicatedStorage</td>
